| 4 | BUG | Low | 108 | Same dead code — inner tab-prefix branch is unreachable |
| 5 | QUESTION | Medium | 76 | `lines[0:len(lines)-2]` can panic with slice bounds out of range if few lines accumulated |
| 6 | QUESTION | Low | 75 | `"panic(0x"` heuristic is tied to Go runtime internals and may break across versions |

